	<h1 class="title">在讨论脂肪到底健不健康之前，我们得先看那些提出饮食建议的机构到底科不科学</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Aaron E. Carroll</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-22 17:30:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/16451/medium/16451.jpg?1445500107" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


